function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.ini')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.ini', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_73();
if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.ini')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.ini');
} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.ini') != 'fade9818fa5f2e308c857a1a99c33f9a08cafe54') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.ini');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.ini', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/001_ra_base/manifest.ini');
}

if (!is_file('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/test/test_database_plugins.php');
	writefile_112();
	if (!is_file('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/test/test_database_plugins.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php') != '158acfbf78576e1f3185a4cd7df82218866c912d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/test/test_database_plugins.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/test/test_database_plugins.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php') !== '158acfbf78576e1f3185a4cd7df82218866c912d') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php') !== '8cd6f4fe467daa701eb75824adbf0814b2d32294') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/test/test_database_plugins.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_112();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test/test_database_plugins.php') !== '158acfbf78576e1f3185a4cd7df82218866c912d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/test/test_database_plugins.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') != 'f35dc8be336ca2ec3b04a0ac5ef554cc0acdc684') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');

	}

	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== 'f35dc8be336ca2ec3b04a0ac5ef554cc0acdc684') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== '1b405fcbeef3af7fd9b1a5534afdbff3974fcdc8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_123();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== 'f35dc8be336ca2ec3b04a0ac5ef554cc0acdc684') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	writefile_127();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != 'f5a0cf91ca435c9c2d0410ff075d84d242f2cf61') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'f5a0cf91ca435c9c2d0410ff075d84d242f2cf61') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'd2042f94ce8c91a61ebebb5022fd692768aa987f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_127();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'f5a0cf91ca435c9c2d0410ff075d84d242f2cf61') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
	writefile_140();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php') != '15842253d4896b30a30ac611279ed95ca0fe1dd1') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/http_class.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php') !== '15842253d4896b30a30ac611279ed95ca0fe1dd1') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php') !== 'aa54edbe8515768795ce36586eeae2fb66111f7f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/http_class.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/http_class.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_140();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php') !== '15842253d4896b30a30ac611279ed95ca0fe1dd1') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.js.php');
	writefile_145();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') != '39efd906b5761d1165eae0378bd6618e8fac6e6d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.js.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.js.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '39efd906b5761d1165eae0378bd6618e8fac6e6d') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '9146e42efe64180ffb7d7beb576c4f2deecdb21a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.js.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.js.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.js.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.js.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_145();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '39efd906b5761d1165eae0378bd6618e8fac6e6d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
		}
	}
}

	if (!is_file('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php') != '8c1216de7dbab577312b8d0669ea163437bbbc92') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php') !== '8c1216de7dbab577312b8d0669ea163437bbbc92') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php') !== 'b4ef698023fe5c20bb91a5b61e3ea7868ea483db') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_149();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php') !== '8c1216de7dbab577312b8d0669ea163437bbbc92') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/struct_with_examples.sql.php');
		}
	}
}
